{% comment %}
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
  AI Asuka Stylist — Shopify Theme Embed
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
  
  HOW TO ADD:
  1. Go to Shopify Admin → Online Store → Themes → Edit Code
  2. Open layout/theme.liquid
  3. Paste this snippet just BEFORE the closing </body> tag
  4. Replace YOUR_VERCEL_URL with your actual Vercel deployment URL
  
  OR: Create a new snippet file called "asuka-ai-stylist.liquid"
  and render it in theme.liquid with: {% render 'asuka-ai-stylist' %}
{% endcomment %}

<!-- AI Asuka Stylist Widget -->
<script
  src="https://YOUR_VERCEL_URL.vercel.app/widget.js"
  defer
  id="asuka-ai-stylist-script"
></script>
